# Exception: commit the synthetic demo database so the hosted app has data on
# first load. Streamlit Community Cloud does not run the on-boot setup_db build
# (read-only app filesystem), so the DB ships in the repo. It holds only
# synthetic fintech data — no secrets, no personal data.
